    "body": "yup, let's try it out and see how it feels.  I actually _lightly_ disagree that going into edit mode from shift-enter isn't a good idea, but playing with it in practice is the best way to get a feel for it.  I'll keep an eye on this part of the experience.\n\nI had a bunch of other minor notes I made over the last few weeks, but the recently merged changes  took care of pretty much everything other than this question. It's now feeling really solid, and even if we end up not 100% happy with this one point, it's a very minor one (some of the other issues were more serious).  So in all, looking pretty solid. Awesome job.\n"
